# Ignore Terraform state files and backups in all folders
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.backup

# Ignore all .terraform directories
**/.terraform/

# Ignore variable files that may contain secrets
**/*.tfvars
**/*.auto.tfvars

# Ignore override files
**/*_override.tf
**/*_override.tf.json
**/override.tf
**/override.tf.json

# Ignore crash logs
**/crash.log

# Ignore private key files
**/*.pem
**/*.key
